docs.text: HI THEREE! ¶ Welcome to my MDEF Diary A personal space where I share my journey, my changes, reflections, and everything I’m learning along the way. This diary will be constantly updated: a living space that evolves with me. Through these pages, I’ll try to let you step into my mind, to share my vision and the way I see and interpret the world around me. I hope that exploring it will help you understand my process, my choices. ENJOY
